    slug: 'salon-pos-customer-lifetime-value',
    title: "The Salon Owner's Guide to Tracking Customer Lifetime Value Through Your PoS",
    metaDescription: 'Salon customer lifetime value reveals which clients are worth investing in and which acquisition channels deliver the best long-term returns. Your PoS has the data.',
    cluster: 'PoS Intelligence',
